.TH requirements
.SH DESCRIPTION
Requirements are used to specify requirements needed for some action.
.br
Requirements can be used in various data objects as dialog answers, skills, quests, items to equip/use, trainings.
.br
List requirement directory to see all available requirements.
.br
Requirements can be combined in the requirements block.
.SH XML EXAMPLE
.nf
<reqs>
	<item-req id="imToughWolfMeat1" amount="3"/>
	<flag-req id="flagTest1"/>
</reqs>
